			<h2><a href="http://MadMoneyMachine.com/2014/02/25/mmm-9-empty-gox/" rel="bookmark" title="Permalink a MMM #9: Empty Gox">MMM #9: Empty Gox</a></h2>
			<div>
<p><img class="alignright" title="MMM-009" alt="MMM 2014-01-15" src="http://MadMoneyMachine.com/images/MMMB-009.jpg" width="200" height="200" /></p>
<ul>
<li><span style="line-height: 1.5em;">Bitcoin and Ethereum walk into a bar</span></li>
<li><span style="line-height: 1.5em;">MT Gox&#8217;s woes</span></li>
<li><span style="line-height: 1.5em;"><em>Empty Gox</em> (Sung to the tune </span><em><a style="line-height: 1.5em;" href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/rocky-top-karaoke-version/id272357380?i=272357389">Rocky Top</a></em><span style="line-height: 1.5em;">)</span></li>
<li><span style="line-height: 1.5em;"><strong>Tool</strong>: ZeroBlock for iPhone and Android</span></li>
<li><strong>Altcoin of the Week</strong>: Dogecoin</li>
<li><span style="line-height: 1.5em;">My Dogecoin address: DMyJc3mpBPEjkDiXkYVYKv1XntZQoS7zfU</span></li>
<li><span style="line-height: 1.5em;">Benjamin Lawsky&#8217;s </span><a style="line-height: 1.5em;" href="http://www.reddit.com/r/IAmA/comments/1ygcil/as_requested_im_ben_lawsky_superintendent_of_the/?sort=confidence">AMA</a></li>
<li><a style="line-height: 1.5em;" href="http://business.time.com/2012/01/30/citi-customers-learn-bonus-airline-miles-have-a-high-price/">Tax</a><span style="line-height: 1.5em;"> on Airline miles?</span></li>
<li><span style="line-height: 1.5em;">Bitcoin Fundamentals: BIP 0038 Encryption</span></li>
<li><span style="line-height: 1.5em;">Satoshi&#8217;s Corner: Read section 1: <a href="http://bitcoin.org/bitcoin.pdf">Introduction</a></span></li>
<li><span style="line-height: 1.5em;">Mad Money Machine Call-In 571-366-7121</span></li>
<li><span style="line-height: 1.5em;">Watch out for StealthBit app for mac. <a href="http://securemac.com/Remove-CoinThief-Trojan-Horse-Instructions.php">Removal Instructions</a></span></li>
<li><a style="line-height: 1.5em;" href="http://www.bloomberg.com/video/ebay-paypal-most-successful-together-donahoe-says-M8oKQ3F5Q3SBdIrbWSnzcw.html">PayPal</a><span style="line-height: 1.5em;"> wallet for Bitcoin?</span></li>
<li><span style="line-height: 1.5em;"><strong>Guru</strong>: Winklevii</span></li>
<li><span style="line-height: 1.5em;">Erin Ade on RT talks </span><a style="line-height: 1.5em;" href="http://rt.com/shows/boom-bust/bitcoin-banker-suicide-money-225/">Money Laundering</a></li>
<li><span style="line-height: 1.5em;">Bitpay implements Payment Protocol BIP 70-73</span></li>
<li><strong><span style="line-height: 1.5em;">Merchant of the week: </span></strong><a style="line-height: 1.5em;" href="https://spendbitcoins.com/places/little-olive-tree-bb/">Little Olive Tree</a></li>
<li><strong><span style="line-height: 1.5em;">Market Minute</span></strong></li>
